long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Retro Highway brings the ultimate blend of fast-paced racing and retro vibes directly to your browser. With its pixel-perfect graphics and nostalgic 16-bit style, this endless racing game lets you speed through highways, dodge traffic, and perform high-flying stunts. Collect coins, unlock powerful bikes, and challenge yourself with intense obstacles along the way. Whether you're a fan of arcade classics or looking for a new challenge, Retro Highway offers thrilling gameplay, smooth controls, and endless fun. 

If you have any questions about our Retro Highway game extension or just want to give us some feedback, feel free to send us a message or write a review! We'd love to hear from you. You can mouse over to Support tab on the extension, then click on "visit the developer's support site" to contact us.

If you wish to remove this extension, follow this steps:
1. Click the 3-dot icon at the top-right corner of your screen.
2. Hover your mouse on More tools then click Extensions.
3. Find the Retro Highway extension.
4. Press "Remove"
